  "content": "<h1>Talents</h1>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Talents are by fare the most advanced in the system. It more or less effects everything else in the system.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Figure 1: An example of a talent</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/x6tbKLj/Screenshot-2021-02-19-at-13-42-24.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"1173\" /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: #191813; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">The sheet consists of the following fields:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">An Image<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Name of the Talent<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Below the name is a label that tells you that Item type this is.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Talent groupname: On the Talent page of an actor sheet this represents the grouping name.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; color: #1b1f22;\">Uses: If the talent has the limited number of uses they can be recorded in this section; Uses - is the current number of times the talent has been used. Max - Maximum number of uses for talent.<br /><br /></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Attack Roll Bonuses: Everything effecting you attack roll.<br />Boons/Banes: Do you get a boon or bane bonus to your attack roll.<br />Attributes: What attributes are effected by a boon/bane.<br />Damage: Do you get a damage bonus from this talent.<br />Extra Damage: Do you get an extra damage bonus from this talent if your roll is 20+.<br />Extra Effects: A description of the extra effect. Printed out in the chat window.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Challenge Roll: Boons/Banes bonuses<br />Sometimes certain attributes get boons/banes bonuses.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\"><span style=\"color: #131310; font-family: Helvetica;\">VS Roll: Sometimes a talent requires you to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #131310; font-family: Helvetica;\">succeed on an attribute roll versus an opponent attribute.</span><br />\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; color: #15171a;\">Usually the roll is made with a boons/banes bonuses.<br />The outcome can be some type of damage. You can add multiple types of damage. Damage from a bite and 1d6 of poison etc.<br /><br /></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Healing: The talent can heal and show the option in the char window.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Make a damage roll: The talent just do damage.<br /><br /></li>\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #131310;\">Add bonuses to your characteristics: Simply add a flat bonus to one or more characteristics.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Figure 2: Example an attack in char window with multiple talents activated</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/MgX8smJ/Screenshot-2021-02-19-at-14-30-37.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"267\" height=\"372\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; color: #15171a;\">The system tries to&nbsp;figure out that talents are currently effecting what you are doing. Boons and banes cancels each other out.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
